  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><br></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"机器之心SOTA模型\" data-alias=\"sotaai\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/GU2ibjU7TDkyqTqr59u8fKegUibXxHSW3WF3ib6u8lQO8JicgNbPzicmhb8kPjrkYk6libDSD7ia1RlxQN9bWugwjguOg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"追踪 AI 开源进展，探索先进开发实践。\" data-id=\"MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">①</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">项</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">目：POLAR</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015256\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3574074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7c3304d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwRImbPgAD4hJicsz1Pv941yt8h2g86e5KaIMbK3iczwSQCfPOSPPsj8EiaIrJIKm0gCu6Ml4M6W7HJg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">POLAR是一种通过大规模预训练实现的标量奖励模型的重大突破。它利用创新的POLicy DiscriminAtive LeaRning（POLAR）范式，通过大规模合成语料库有效区分策略。</span>预训练后，POLAR奖励模型通过最小化偏好数据进行微调，快速与人类偏好对齐。POLAR的关键特性包括创新的预训练范式、适用于强化微调、卓越的性能和泛化能力，以及易于定制的预训练检查点。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/polar\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/polar</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">①项目：Observer</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015255\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5694444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=51b2517e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwRImbPgAD4hJicsz1Pv941yGt3mmpcvpZKJTEgXcVdGhEdNls4Vu0S9HpReYoBcLCnGQ3PDUT1Bcw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Observer是一个开源平台，旨在运行本地AI智能体以观察用户屏幕，同时确保数据的隐私和安全。</span>用户可以创建自己的Observer AI智能体，通过配置传感器、模型和工具来实现个性化功能。该平台支持多种输入方式，如屏幕OCR、截图、剪贴板和麦克风等，并提供多种工具来处理模型响应，如发送通知、存储和检索记忆、发送邮件和短信等。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/observer\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/observer</a></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">②项目：TradingAgents</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015257\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8074074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a0d1f6de&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwRImbPgAD4hJicsz1Pv941y5qlbuO5yV1sU0OwSJmBnico0AopnnnGHtduCG9V6Fo0uRv0tlicULhzg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">TradingAgents中文增强版是一个基于多智能体大语言模型的金融交易决策框架，专为中文用户设计。</span>该项目在TauricResearch/TradingAgents的基础上开发，提供完整的中文文档和本地化支持，适应国内网络环境。项目支持A股、港股等中国金融市场，旨在推动AI在中国金融科技领域的应用。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/tradingagents-cn\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/tradingagents-cn</a></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">③项目：Biosphere3</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015258\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.30648148148148147\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f051dfcc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwRImbPgAD4hJicsz1Pv941ysNdQ4MITCTHYibBFbNpiaJuGh1iaic5FueXFs39HgcLOac5Xn3ZL7kcqVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Biosphere3是一个开放式的智能体进化竞技场和大规模多智能体社会模拟实验。</span>受1990年代封闭生态系统项目Biosphere 2的启发，Biosphere3在数字沙盒中模拟现实社会和进化过程。该项目还设计为公民科学游戏，旨在吸引更多智能体和人类参与者。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">其目标是优化通用主权AI智能体的架构，探索数字生命体与人类的共存，并通过模拟社会和文明的演化来教育公众关于智能体和AI技术的知识。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/biosphere3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/biosphere3</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">①项目：POLARIS</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015259\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5814814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=57f5e8f8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwRImbPgAD4hJicsz1Pv941yIW84tbzpRwsOdHHalABNETsA7PGxBk6By6ZsANYyHTdUV3zsQ4yTibQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">POLARIS是一个开源的后训练优化方案，利用强化学习（RL）扩展来进一步优化具有强推理能力的模型。</span>该项目展示了即使是最先进的模型如Qwen3-4B，在通过POLARIS增强后，在复杂推理任务上也能取得显著的提升。通过使用开源数据和学术级资源进行训练，POLARIS将开源推理模型的性能提升到了一个全新的水平。在基准评估中，我们的方法令人惊讶地超越了领先的商业系统如Claude-4-Opus、Grok-3-Beta和o3-mini-high。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/polaris\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/polaris</a></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;text-wrap-style: initial;color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.51px;\">②项目：DLoRAL</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015260\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8435185185185186\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=35fae8d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwRImbPgAD4hJicsz1Pv941yChhctdHg2p2B81RUNae3mGpvcbglq9GhpljgsartpgMyibibpbYpibfqQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(58, 60, 70);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;text-align: start;\">★<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">DLoRAL是一个用于视频超分辨率的项目，旨在通过一步扩散方法实现细节丰富且时间一致的视频超分辨率。</span>该项目由香港理工大学和OPPO研究院的研究人员开发，提供了推理代码和预训练权重。DLoRAL通过动态双阶段训练方案，在优化时间一致性和增强高频空间细节之间交替进行，以确保稳定性。推理过程中，C-LoRA和D-LoRA被合并到冻结的扩散UNet中，实现对低质量输入的一步增强。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/dloral\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/dloral</a></span></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "文章汇总了 2025 年 7 月 9 日发布的六个最新 AI 开源项目，涵盖奖励模型预训练、AI 智能体平台、金融交易框架、社会模拟、后训练优化及视频超分辨率等多个前沿领域。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章汇总了 2025 年 7 月 9 日发布的六个最新 AI 开源项目，涵盖奖励模型预训练、AI 智能体平台、金融交易框架、社会模拟、后训练优化及视频超分辨率等多个前沿领域。",
  "summary": "该文章是一篇针对 2025 年 7 月 9 日最新开源项目的汇总报告，精选并简要介绍了六个在人工智能领域具有代表性的项目。其中，POLAR 通过创新的预训练范式实现大规模奖励模型，能通过合成语料库有效区分策略，并快速与人类偏好对齐，适用于强化微调；Observer 是一个开源的本地 AI 智能体平台，强调用户隐私和数据安全，支持多种输入和工具集成，允许用户创建个性化智能体；TradingAgents 是专为中文用户设计，基于多智能体大语言模型的金融交易决策框架，支持中国金融市场；Biosphere3 则是一个开放式的智能体进化竞技场，用于大规模多智能体社会模拟实验，旨在优化通用主权 AI 智能体架构；POLARIS 作为后训练优化方案，利用强化学习扩展，能显著提升模型在复杂推理任务上的性能，甚至超越部分商业系统；DLoRAL 则专注于通过一步扩散方法实现细节丰富且时间一致的视频超分辨率。文章旨在快速向读者呈现 AI 领域的最新技术进展和开源实践。",
